+/*
+ * Allwinner A83T and H3 HDMI lowlevel functions
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2016 Jean-Francois Moine <moinejf@free.fr>
+ * Adapted from the sun8iw6 and sun8iw7 disp2 drivers
+ *	Copyright (c) 2016 Allwinnertech Co., Ltd.
+ *
